# Copy to `.env` in this folder (`.env` is gitignored).
# Used by: npm run publish:open-vsx
#
# Save this file as UTF-8 (in VS Code: click encoding on the status bar → “Save with Encoding” → UTF-8).
# Create the token at: https://open-vsx.org/user-settings/tokens
# The GitHub account / Eclipse account that owns the token must be allowed to publish your publisher (e.g. wideshot).
OVSX_PAT=
